    <published>2024-06-08T01:43:04.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-06-08T01:46:54.772Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>アマエミ -longing for you-</p><p>主人公锅岛立哉曾经是世界知名的画家。<br>然而由于某些原因离开了画坛，当起了社会科学教师，过着与画界无缘的日子。</p><p>在象牙之塔的社会科学办公室，与小猫离群索居地过着幽隐般的生活。<br>不过，随着新学期的开始，清新的凉风拂面而来。</p><p>敬仰立哉的时髦女学生楠木彩华。<br>神秘地邀请立哉，学校最优秀的才女来栖樱绫。<br>以及恩师的女儿明日咲沙希。</p><p>心如死灰般褪色的人生，开始因为三名少女变得五彩缤纷。</p><p><img src="https://img.touchgalres.xyz/2024/06/e7771e068e20240601231120.png"></img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E3%80%91/%E6%B5%AE%E5%A3%AB%E5%BE%B7galgame%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/%E6%B5%AE%E5%A3%AB%E5%BE%B7galgame%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86-1/2022%E5%B9%B46%E6%9C%88/%5B220624%5D%5B%E3%81%82%E3%81%96%E3%82%89%E3%81%97%E3%81%9D%E3%81%B5%E3%81%A8%5D%20%E3%82%A2%E3%83%9E%E3%82%A8%E3%83%9F%20-longing%20for%20you-%20DL%E7%89%88%20(files).rar"   title="PC"><i class="red larger"></i><span>PC</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%BD%92%20%E6%A1%A3%E3%80%91/%E3%80%90Tyranor%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E3%80%91/%E3%82%A2%E3%83%9E%E3%82%A8%E3%83%9F%20-longing%20for%20you-%E3%80%90%E6%9C%BA%E7%BF%BB%E3%80%91.rar"   title="Ty"><i class="red larger"></i><span>Ty</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1SybQlqrGxK9Z4JwXAOmuIw?pwd=94oy?"   title="补丁提取码94oy"><i class="red larger"></i><span>补丁提取码94oy</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
