  <entry>
    <title>【PC,KR】恋爱x决胜战</title>
    <link href="https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/c64749c8.html"/>
    <id>https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/c64749c8.html</id>
    <published>2024-05-31T09:37:39.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-31T09:58:10.550Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>「我，转学生花丸茉莉喜欢小町浩孝！请和我交往！」</p><p>受到学妹挑衅，</p><p>被学生会长搭讪，</p><p>又被偶像追着跑——</p><p>每天都活得很随意的主角『小町浩孝』。</p><p>就在这时候，转学生突如其来的告白——</p><p>因为她的一番话，</p><p>让长久停滞的主角争夺战，再次引燃战火。</p><p>「为什么把我晾在一旁，跟来路不明的女人卿卿我我啊！你已经不管我了吗」</p><p>「学长……只要是学长说的……不管是什么莲菜都愿意听哦」</p><p>「我得不到哥哥的爱，都是这群围在哥哥身旁的母猪的错」</p><p>在主角本人不知情的状况下，</p><p>女生们展开既丑陋又无谓，却极其认真的恋爱生死战！</p><p>胜利的女神究竟会对谁微笑呢！？</p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/11/583216b65320231125015946.jpg"></img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E5%8D%97%2B6TBgal%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8B%E7%A0%81south-plus/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%BD%AE%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86/Others/%5BASa%20Project%5D%20%E6%81%8B%E6%84%9B%C3%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%AF%E3%82%A4%E3%82%A2%E3%83%AB%20%20%E6%81%8B%E7%88%B1%C3%97%E5%86%B3%E8%83%9C%E6%88%98%20%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%89%88%5B%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E5%B1%8BJ.TEST%E7%89%B9A%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E7%BB%84%5D/%5BASa%20Project%5D%20%E6%81%8B%E6%84%9B%C3%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%AF%E3%82%A4%E3%82%A2%E3%83%AB%20%20%E6%81%8B%E7%88%B1%C3%97%E5%86%B3%E8%83%9C%E6%88%98%20%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%89%88%5B%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E5%B1%8BJ.TEST%E7%89%B9A%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E7%BB%84%5D.rar"   title="PC"><i class="red larger"></i><span>PC</span></a><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/puppet%20studio/Galgame/%E6%81%8B%E7%88%B1%C3%97%E5%86%B3%E8%83%9C%E6%88%98/KR_%E6%81%8B%E7%88%B1x%E5%86%B3%E8%83%9C%E6%88%98_%E6%AD%A5%E5%85%B5%E7%89%88.rar"   title="KR解压码木偶"><i class="red larger"></i><span>KR解压码木偶</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
